This directory contains some useful bits and pieces related to cvmfs.

cvmfs.spec
The spec file we use to create an RPM containing the cvmfs client part.

cvmfs-server.spec
The spec files for packaging the server tools (without kernel module)

cvmfs-lvmrotate
A wrapper script for LVM to deal with repository snapshots.  This script is part of the example release manager machine for small VOs as descripbed in the cvmfs technical report.

webfs.conf
Example configuration for Apache to publish a repository.  This script is part of the example release manager machine for small VOs as descripbed in the
cvmfs technical report.

cernvm_rsa.pub
Master public key for verifying file catalogs 
